data.title: Companion of the Order of St Michael and St George (CMG)
data.meta_description: The Most Distinguished Order of Saint Michael and Saint George is the sixth most senior in the British honours system. It is awarded to persons who have rendered important services to Commonweatlh or foreign nations. Companion, is the most junior of the three classes in this Order.
data.text:
The Airborne Shop is the official shop of Support Our Paras (The Parachute Regiment Charity RCN1131977).

Profits from all sales made through our shop go directly to Support Our Paras, so every purchase you make with us will directly benefit The Parachute Regiment and Airborne Forces.
